name: Warfighter - Victory - 4th Edition
additionalNotes: This Victory cigar is Warfighter Tobacco's fourth edition of the Victory Cigar.  Each production run is done in a small batch to maximize flavor and feel.  The 4th Edition is a closed foot cigar with a torpedo cap. It has a Brazilian Mata Fina wrapper with Nicaraguan fillers. This cigar changes flavor a couple times while you smoke it. It is available only in 6x54 closed foot, torpedo and is very limited production. So if you have to celebrate a Victory with a premium cigar, the Victory cigar is the best we have to offer.
